{"id":1688,"date":"2024-12-12T13:38:41","date_gmt":"2024-12-12T21:38:41","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/prowler.com\/?page_id=1688"},"modified":"2024-12-13T18:39:03","modified_gmt":"2024-12-14T02:39:03","slug":"prowler-5","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/prowler.com\/prowler-5\/","title":{"rendered":"Prowler 5"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignwide size-full\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"640\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Mastering-Multi-Cloud-1-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1743\" srcset=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Mastering-Multi-Cloud-1-1.png 640w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Mastering-Multi-Cloud-1-1-600x188.png 600w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Mastering-Multi-Cloud-1-1-150x47.png 150w, https:\/\/prowler.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Mastering-Multi-Cloud-1-1-346x108.png 346w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group mb-50 mt-35\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\"><div \n    class=\"block--carousel mt-8 relative\"    x-data=\"carousel(1)\"\n>\n    <header class=\"relative\">\n        <h2 class=\"h2\"><\/h2>\n    <\/header>\n    <div class=\"carousel-slider mt-10 flex gap-5 w-full overflow-x-scroll snap-x snap-mandatory items-start\">\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p id=\"agenda\">Toni de la Fuente\u2014creator of Prowler\u2014will walk through the new features and share practical tips for using Prowler to strengthen your security posture across clouds. Expect a straightforward look at how Prowler 5 empowers teams with:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Multi-cloud support: <\/strong>One platform to assess security across AWS, Azure, GCP, and Kubernetes.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Upgraded UI and API tools:<\/strong> Making security management smoother for DevOps and security teams.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Automation-ready workflows:<\/strong> For faster assessments and better integration with your existing processes.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Continuous monitoring: <\/strong>So you can detect and fix issues before they become problems.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"agenda\">If you\u2019re looking for a security solution that scales with your cloud strategy, this is the webinar for you. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"agenda\"><strong>Why Prowler 5?<\/strong> Because it\u2019s open source, customizable, and purpose-built for teams who want transparency and flexibility in their security tools. Sign up now to join us live\u2014or register to receive the recording if you can\u2019t make it.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wpforms-container wpforms-block wpforms-block-a08537db-f7b6-4365-96b3-725fa3481934 wpforms-render-modern\" id=\"wpforms-1730\"><form id=\"wpforms-form-1730\" class=\"wpforms-validate wpforms-form wpforms-ajax-form\" data-formid=\"1730\" method=\"post\" enctype=\"multipart\/form-data\" action=\"\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1688\" data-token=\"6ff3bdff376d5f853295ce07818a6270\" data-token-time=\"1747897320\"><div class=\"wpforms-head-container\"><div class=\"wpforms-description\">Register to join our webinar on Dec. 18th @ 9 am PST | Noon EST for an in-depth demo of Prowler 5 and its new capabilities. <\/div><